---
title: Crumbed Chicken & Bacon Jam Sambo with Cos Salad & Parmesan
description: A gourmet sandwich combo is the perfect solution for when you want something special but you’re short on time. This one
might be our new favourite; golden crumbed chicken, a creamy dressed salad, sharp cheddar and a glorious onion and bacon
jam are all nestled between two slices of crunchy and soft sourdough. Go on, take a bite!

